amazing dance song ! to tell you the truth , i can not find words to explain why this song is so amazing . the first time i heard the album version , i was like `` why choosing clocks , phones and abba samples for a first single ? what is madonna thinking ? '' after buying this single and hearing it loud at home , i could not stop dancing ( specially the stuart price remix ) . there is a feeling of `` leting go , forget your problems , feel free '' , not easy to describe everytime you hear it and dance to it . even after , you will find yourself saying `` time goes by , so slowly , so slowly , so slowly ...